@startuml integration-pipeline
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam ArrowColor #555
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #EEF2FF
  BorderColor #3F51B5
  FontColor #212121
}
skinparam swimlane {
  BorderColor #9E9E9E
  TitleBackgroundColor #E0E0E0
  TitleFontColor #212121
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  BorderColor #F9A825
}

title Pipeline de Integração — Sprint 1 Build & Test

|#E3F2FD| Developer |
start
:Edita HCL / código fonte;

|#E8F5E9| Go Toolchain |
:go run cmd/gen-tfstate\n--count=50000 --seed=42;
note right: gera fixture.tfstate.json (2.6MB)

:go test ./...\n-run TestParseTFState;
note right
  PRT-01 Unit Tests:
  · Timing < 500ms ✅
  · Byte count ✅
  · ID spot-check ✅
  · Nil guards ✅
end note

:go build -buildmode=c-shared\n-o libbridge.so;
note right: Produz libbridge.so (2.9MB)\n+ bridge.h (header C)

|#FFF3E0| Zig Toolchain |
:zig build bench\n(ReleaseFast);
note right
  PRT-02 SoA vs AoS:
  AoS avg: 70µs
  SoA avg:  5µs
  Speedup: 12.45× ✅
end note

:zig build test\n-Dbridge-path=../go-bridge;
note right
  PRT-01 Integration:
  (requer LD_LIBRARY_PATH)
  ⚠ pendente configuração
  de runtime linker
end note

|#F3E5F5| CI / Verificação |
if (Todos os gates passaram?) then (sim)
  :Sprint 1 PASS\nAvança para Sprint 2;
  stop
else (não)
  :Falha registrada\nno journal;
  :Retorna ao desenvolvimento;
  stop
endif
@enduml
